{"tid":1745240,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"青年涉連環打劫至少3名性工作者","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T10:16:30.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3d44eaeca241d461f6bd48256f7a91c36e4ab6cb","tid":1745240,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.tdm.com.mo/c_radio/news/news_img/201911221201545dd75db22782d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tdm.com.mo%2Fc_radio%2Fnews%2Fnews_img%2F201911221201545dd75db22782d.jpg&h=002b2b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(澳門電台消息) 司警拘捕 1名27歲本澳青年，他懷疑針對性工作者行劫，同日連續至少 3次犯案。<br />\n<br />\n司警在星期二 (19日) 接獲1名20多歲的內地女子報案，稱透過手機聊天軟件認識 1名男子，在新口岸的酒店客房與對方性交易後，這名男子隨即用鎅刀要脅，搶走她 2部共值 8,000多元的手提電話。<br />\n<br />\n司警調查後，相信當日大約 2小時內，另有 2名懷疑賣淫女子遇劫，但沒有報案，分別損失 2條頸鏈和 5,000元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n涉案青年昨日 (21日) 經關閘口岸入境時被截獲。有人聲稱因為欠債犯案，劫走的 2部手機已在內地變賣。 (黃偉昌  黃偉鴻)"},{"pid":"4351ac37e642523dc35ddeca472bd49846a86618","tid":1745240,"uid":6248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"16d930f729c6704fbb070396e118678eb44f25be","tid":1745240,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4351ac37e642523dc35ddeca472bd49846a86618","tid":1745240,"uid":6248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"識玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:24:15.000Z","msg":"另有 2名懷疑賣淫女子遇劫，但沒有報案"},{"pid":"587f026f2b0a470a10ea82615967f6d08883860e","tid":1745240,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:28:46.000Z","msg":"@NBxn"},{"pid":"e65c95db3c14aacc2905907f59f0a540fe4eb4d6","tid":1745240,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:30:29.000Z","msg":"係咪玄學大師詹惟中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbbea84ac6fa77a2587583a763635f93d01121c","tid":1745240,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike